in the event of the application gives u an error:
NumberFormatter not found
do the following; 
1. Goto your php.ini file in your linux server and edit the folowing:
a. enable the intl extension
#udo 
extension=intl

b. set the language for the error messages for that intl extension
# udo : i did this
intl.default_locale = EN_US

c. configure the error level
# udo : i did this
intl.error_level = E_WARNING


